ta\";s:6:\"Joomla\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"guid\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:27:\"http://logichunt.com/?p=386\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:1:{s:11:\"isPermaLink\";s:5:\"false\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:11:\"description\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:494:\"Joomla is a free and open-source content management system (CMS) for publishing web content. It is built on a model–view–controller web application framework that can be used independently of the CMS. There are many free Joomla extensions in the Joomla gallery for the betterment of your site. But it is always a challenge to find...  <a href=\"http://logichunt.com/download-best-free-joomla-extension/\" class=\"more-link\" title=\"Read Download Best Free Joomla Extension\">Read more &#187;</a>\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:9:\"LogicHunt\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:6887:\"<p>Joomla is a free and open-source content management system (CMS) for publishing web content. It is built on a model–view–controller web application framework that can be used independently of the CMS.</p>\n<p>There are many free Joomla extensions in the Joomla gallery for the betterment of your site. But it is always a challenge to find and combine the right extensions for your Joomla project. On this website you can preview and download my free extensions. I try to create simple, easy to use extensions and keep them up to date. From all free Joomla extensions I have made a great list of it.</p>\n<h3>1. Akeeba Backup:</h3>\n<p><strong>Includes: Component, Module, Plugin</strong><br />\n<strong>Compatibility: 3</strong></p>\n<p>Akeeba Backup Core is the most widely used open-source backup component for the Joomla! CMS. Its mission is simple: create a site backup that can be restored on any Joomla!-capable server, making it ideal not only for backups but also for site transfers or even deploying sites to your clients&#8217; servers. Akeeba Backup creates a full backup of your site in a single archive.</p>\n<p>Details: http://extensions.joomla.org/extensions/extension/access-a-security/site-security/akeeba-backup</p>\n<h3>2. AcyMailing Starter:</h3>\n<p><strong>Includes: Component, Module, Plugin</strong><br />\n<strong>Compatibility: 3</strong></p>\n<p>AcyMailing is a reliable Newsletter and email marketing extension for Joomla.<br />\nAcyMailing enables you to efficiently manage an unlimited number of subscribers, organize them into mailing lists, send personalized newsletters.</p>\n<p>Details: http://extensions.joomla.org/extensions/extension/marketing/newsletter/acymailing-starter</p>\n<h3>3. JEvents:</h3>\n<p><strong>Includes: Component, Module, Plugin</strong><br />\n<strong>Compatibility: 3</strong></p>\n<p>JEvents is a well known and Loved Events Calendar / Management solution for Joomla. JEvents provides a full events and calendar solution for your Joomla! site. Showing your events in listings or as a visual monthly calendar view, create complex repeats patterns, import and export your events with a couple of clicks, offer a feed with your latest events&#8230; And also with more than 40 languages translated, we are likely to have a translation for your website.</p>\n<p>Details: http://extensions.joomla.org/extensions/extension/calendars-a-events/events/jevents</p>\n<h3>4. HikaShop:</h3>\n<p><strong>Includes: Component, Module, Plugin</strong><br />\n<strong>Compatibility: 3</strong></p>\n<p>HikaShop is an E-Commerce extension for Joomla 1.5, 2.5 and 3.x. It is built for simplicity and flexibility.<br />\nHikaShop also has a wide range of marketing tools, but also powerful statistics displayable on your HikaShop dashboard to help you manage your store. It provides advanced taxes, zones, languages and currencies management for worldwide sales as well as advanced customization capabilities of your online shop in order to meet your website ecommerce needs.</p>\n<p>Details: http://extensions.joomla.org/extensions/extension/e-commerce/shopping-cart/hikashop</p>\n<h3>5. Admin Tools:</h3>\n<p><strong>Includes: Component, Module, Plugin</strong><br />\n<strong>Compatibility: 3</strong></p>\n<p>Admin Tools is a true Swiss Army knife for your site. Our freely available Admin Tools Core will detect, notify you about new Joomla! releases, fix your files&#8217; and directories&#8217; permissions, protect your administrator directory with a password, change your database prefix, migrate links pointing to your old domain on-the-fly and perform database maintenance, all with a single click.</p>\n<p>http://extensions.joomla.org/extensions/extension/access-a-security/site-security/admin-tools</p>\n<h3>6. Event Gallery:</h3>\n<p><strong>Includes: Component, Plugin</strong><br />\n<strong>Compatibility: 3</strong></p>\n<p>Event Gallery is an easy to use gallery component. It supports adaptive, flexible and responsive layouts and provides a unique way of presenting images. If presenting is not enough enable the cart! Let users browse through your images and buy them.</p>\n<p>Details: http://extensions.joomla.org/extensions/extension/photos-a-images/galleries/event-gallery</p>\n<h3>7. Creative Contact Form:</h3>\n<p><strong>Includes: Component, Module, Plugin</strong><br />\n<strong>Compatibility: 3</strong></p>\n<p>Creative Contact Form is a powerful contact form generator with amazing visual effects. You will be surprised by count of all the possible features! Over 67,000+ sites are already using Creative Contact Form.</p>\n<p>http://extensions.joomla.org/extensions/extension/contacts-and-feedback/contact-forms/creative-contact-form</p>\n<h3>8. GMapFP : Google Map:</h3>\n<p><strong>Includes: Component, Module, Plugin</strong><br />\n<strong>Compatibility: 3</strong></p>\n<p>Thanks to GMapFP, you can use Google Maps very easily in your Joomla site. This component is natively compatible with Joomla and is available French and English. It&#8217;s compatible with JoomFish, XMAP, JComments and Joomla search module. GMapFP is translated in many languages.</p>\n<p>Details: http://extensions.joomla.org/extensions/extension/maps-a-weather/maps-a-locations/gmapfp-google-map</p>\n<h3>9. All Video Share:</h3>\n<p><strong>Includes: Component, Module, Plugin</strong><br />\n<strong>Compatibility: 3</strong></p>\n<p>A complete and flexible video share solution for Joomla with a wide range of features. Support all major Joomla versions, Support responsive templates, Handle variety of Media formats that flash can handle such as flv, mp4, 3g2, 3gp, aac, f4b, f4p, f4v, m4a, m4v, mov(h.264), sdp, vp6. HTML5 fallback. Color the skin on your Own.<br />\nFlexible options to add Videos either by simply providing Video URL (or) using UPLOAD method. Youtube API to play Youtube videos.</p>\n<p>Details: http://extensions.joomla.org/extensions/extension/multimedia/multimedia-players/allvideoshare</p>\n<h3>10. Tag Meta:</h3>\n<p><strong>Includes: Component, Plugin</strong><br />\n<strong>Compatibility: 3</strong></p>\n<p>Tag Meta allows to efficiently manage all site&#8217;s meta information. With Tag Meta, as example, it is possible to set the tag &#8216;title&#8217; or the meta tags (e.g. from the most common &#8216;description&#8217;, &#8216;keywords&#8217;, &#8216;robots&#8217;, as well as the recently &#8216;content rights&#8217; and &#8216;external reference&#8217;) or link &#8216;canonical&#8217; on any page, just specifying the URL or a part of it. This provides a swiss army knife to improve site positioning in SEO optimization. But Tag Meta also supports regular expressions in the matching rules and this allows to match a group of URLs with a single rule. In this way it is possible to manage metadata from a single control panel.</p>\n<p>Details: http://extensions.joomla.org/extensions/extension/site-management/seo-a-metadata/tag-meta</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:62:\"http://logichunt.com/download-best-free-joomla-extension/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1:\"0\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:30:\"com-wordpress:feed-additions:1\";a:1:{s:7:\"post-id\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:3:\"386\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:4;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:48:\"\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n				\n		\n		\n\n		\n		\n				\n			\n		\n		\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:6:{s:0:\"\";a:7:{s:5:\"title\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:60:\"Top and Best Joomla Extension for Easier and Better Websites\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:82:\"http://logichunt.com/top-and-best-joomla-extension-for-easier-and-better-websites/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:90:\"http://logichunt.com/top-and-best-joomla-extension-for-easier-and-better-websites/#respond\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:7:\"pubDate\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:31:\"Fri, 15 Jul 2016 17:53:02 +0000\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"category\";a:3:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:11:\"Latest News\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:1;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:9:\"Extension\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:2;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:6:\"Joomla\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"guid\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:27:\"http://logichunt.com/?p=384\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:1:{s:11:\"isPermaLink\";s:5:\"false\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:11:\"description\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:553:\"Joomla is a free and open-source content management system (CMS) for publishing web content. It is built on a model–view–controller web application framework that can be used independently of the CMS. It&#8217;s an opportune time to take a look at some of the more popular Joomla extensions and see how they perform. Specifically, I looked...  <a href=\"http://logichunt.com/top-and-best-joomla-extension-for-easier-and-better-websites/\" class=\"more-link\" title=\"Read Top and Best Joomla Extension for Easier and Better Websites\">Read more &#187;</a>\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:9:\"LogicHunt\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:3705:\"<p>Joomla is a free and open-source content management system (CMS) for publishing web content. It is built on a model–view–controller web application framework that can be used independently of the CMS.</p>\n<p>It&#8217;s an opportune time to take a look at some of the more popular Joomla extensions and see how they perform. Specifically, I looked at how they run on Joomla 2.5, the current &#8220;stable&#8221; release of Joomla. Joomla 3.0, which was released on September 27, 2012, has a lot of great features going for it, but the module ecosystem will still need some time to catch up. If you have moved to version 3.0, check with each specific extension&#8217;s website to make sure it&#8217;s compatible.</p>\n<h3>Community Builder:</h3>\n<p><strong>Includes: Component, Module, Plugin </strong><br />\n<strong>Compatibility: 3 </strong></p>\n<p>Community Builder (CB) is an extremely flexible and robust social networking solution for Joomla. CB has a huge user base, a long history and a great future. Social websites go far beyond Facebook look-alikes and CB has literally hundreds of built-in features and can be extended with extra (free or commercial) add-ons from the CB Team and other parties that will help you realize your very own &#8211; tailored to your specific needs &#8211; social networking website.</p>\n<p>There are lots of community-oriented packages out there for Joomla, with many different approaches to introducing elements of community site management into a site. For flexibility, Community Builder from Joomlapolis seems the current favorite.</p>\n<p>Details: http://extensions.joomla.org/extension/community-builder</p>\n<h3>JCE:</h3>\n<p><strong>Includes: Component, Module, Plugin </strong><br />\n<strong>Compatibility: 3 </strong></p>\n<p>An award-winning, configurable WYSIWYG editor for Joomla! based on Moxiecode&#8217;s TinyMCE. Includes advanced Image/Media, File and Link handling, plugin support, and an Administration interface for editor configuration.</p>\n<p>I like my writing tools very simple and free from distraction. I need to focus on the words themselves, not all the dandified formatting and alignment tools that can be a big distraction. That&#8217;s why I like tools like GNU Emacs or iA Writer depending on the platform I&#8217;m using, and that&#8217;s why I can appreciate using the default editor within Joomla, TinyMCE. TinyMCE is simple, has some straightforward formatting tools, and there you are.</p>\n<p>Details: http://extensions.joomla.org/extension/jce</p>\n<h3>K2:</h3>\n<p><strong>Includes: Component, Module, Plugin </strong><br />\n<strong>Compatibility: 3 </strong></p>\n<p>The powerful award-winning content extension for Joomla with more than 2 million downloads (and counting)!</p>\n<p>K2 is an advanced component for creating more detailed Joomla! articles with images, videos, image galleries and attachments. It is developed by JoomlaWorks. K2 steps in to fill the gap that exists in the Joomla framework. It offers a robust and expansive set of features that allow you to manage your content more easily than you would with default Joomla. The K2 extension for Joomla supports article management, tags, comments, image galleries and video management, content modules, and a cool drag and drop Media Manager. Besides that, K2 comes with a set of friendly templates that allow you to implement a module without messing around with the template’s code. Equipped with more plugins to create rich content, K2 even enables converting a normal news site into an author’s blog, product catalog, download manager, product showcase and many more magic to amaze your clients.</p>\n<p>Details: http://extensions.joomla.org/extension/k2</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:87:\"http://logichunt.com/top-and-best-joomla-extension-for-easier-and-better-websites/feed/\";s:7:\"